{"word":"ἀναχώρησις","slug":"ἀναχώρησις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναχώρησις</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀναχωρέω'><el>ἀναχωρέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a drawing back, retiring, retreating</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a means</i> or <i>place of retreat, refuge</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}